@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v2 + wp.cos((v2 + 0.40 * v2 + 0.32)))
    tmp = (0.81 - tmp)
    v1 = 0.13
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.49) * 0.45) * v2)
    data[tid] = v0
